the Su family likely won't act rashly soon.

53
00:03:07,820 --> 00:03:10,140
For now, we must prioritize safety.

54
00:03:27,220 --> 00:03:28,060
Uncle,

55
00:03:28,860 --> 00:03:30,700
you said the person accidentally

56
00:03:30,700 --> 00:03:31,940
discovered Pei Chufeng.

57
00:03:33,500 --> 00:03:34,580
Why didn't she

58
00:03:35,260 --> 00:03:37,380
stay to investigate

59
00:03:37,740 --> 00:03:39,260
or report to the authorities?

60
00:03:39,780 --> 00:03:42,620
Instead, she hurriedly took him away.

61
00:03:44,300 --> 00:03:46,340
She wanted to protect him.

62
00:03:46,700 --> 00:03:48,100
I think this matter

63
00:03:49,060 --> 00:03:50,940
is connected to the Pei family.

64
00:03:52,060 --> 00:03:53,540
If it really is the Pei family,

65
00:03:54,260 --> 00:03:56,900
then Pei Chufeng is probably at their place.

66
00:03:59,260 --> 00:04:01,620
