without full confidence.

80
00:04:31,460 --> 00:04:32,620
Now, both families

81
00:04:32,900 --> 00:04:34,860
have to feign ignorance

82
00:04:35,300 --> 00:04:36,500
and keep the peace.

83
00:04:36,780 --> 00:04:37,780
Yes, yes.

84
00:04:38,500 --> 00:04:39,700
We can't do that.

85
00:04:41,340 --> 00:04:42,180
Come in.

86
00:04:47,060 --> 00:04:48,660
Young Master, something happened.

87
00:04:48,660 --> 00:04:49,860
