91
00:04:55,060 --> 00:04:55,940
What happened?

92
00:04:56,260 --> 00:04:57,380
I don't know.

93
00:04:57,580 --> 00:04:58,900
Before we found Ms. Shuangshuang,

94
00:04:58,900 --> 00:04:59,890
their bodies were discovered

95
00:04:59,890 --> 00:05:01,020
in an alley in the West Market.

96
00:05:01,020 --> 00:05:02,420
No clues were left behind.

97
00:05:03,100 --> 00:05:04,340
