104
00:05:25,020 --> 00:05:27,580
before seeing you again.

105
00:05:33,780 --> 00:05:35,260
Do you know Shan Jingtian?

106
00:05:35,740 --> 00:05:36,780
Do you know who tricked him

107
00:05:36,980 --> 00:05:39,540
into stealing the Crown?

108
00:05:40,100 --> 00:05:41,100
The Crown?

109
00:05:41,160 --> 00:05:42,060
The Crown?

110
00:05:42,060 --> 00:05:43,420
It wasn't me.

111
00:05:43,420 --> 00:05:44,700
I didn't steal the Crown.

112
00:05:44,700 --> 00:05:45,860
- I didn't steal it.
- It's okay.

113
00:05:45,860 --> 00:05:46,820
I didn't steal it.

114
00:05:46,820 --> 00:05:47,820
Ms. Shan,

115
00:05:48,180 --> 00:05:50,020
I've heard about your grievances

116
00:05:50,380 --> 00:05:51,820
about the Su and Pei families.

117
00:05:55,260 --> 00:05:57,260
I've been at the Pei's Mansion for decades.

118
00:05:57,260 --> 00:05:59,580
I've seen everything.

119
00:05:59,980 --> 00:06:01,540
I have no right to speak up,

120
00:06:02,420 --> 00:06:05,220
but now that the master is alive,

121
00:06:05,980 --> 00:06:08,300
I want to defend him a bit.

122
00:06:09,380 --> 00:06:11,220
When the Crown was lost,

123
00:06:11,220 --> 00:06:13,380
the City Lord was on the verge
of losing his position,

124
00:06:14,180 --> 00:06:16,420
and Yuncui City was on the brink of collapse.

125
00:06:16,740 --> 00:06:18,500
But at that moment,

126
00:06:18,500 --> 00:06:20,900
Suyu Pavilion presented

127
00:06:20,900 --> 00:06:22,940
a replacement Crown,

128
00:06:23,380 --> 00:06:25,420
saving Yuncui City

129
00:06:25,740 --> 00:06:27,820
and earning immense fame.

130
00:06:28,820 --> 00:06:30,220
But think about it.

131
00:06:31,140 --> 00:06:32,580
How could they create

132
00:06:32,780 --> 00:06:35,460
such a royal tribute

133
00:06:35,460 --> 00:06:37,420
in just a few days?

134
00:06:37,780 --> 00:06:41,140
It's obvious someone had premeditated this.

135
00:06:41,580 --> 00:06:44,340
Now, with the master found
in the Su family's dungeon,

136
00:06:44,820 --> 00:06:46,820
the mastermind behind all this

137
00:06:47,060 --> 00:06:49,420
should be clear to you, Ms. Shuangshuang.

138
00:06:50,860 --> 00:06:53,180
I don't need to say more.

139
00:07:00,740 --> 00:07:01,580
Shuangshuang,

140
00:07:02,140 --> 00:07:03,420
I know you've been

141
00:07:04,220 --> 00:07:06,220
bearing all this alone for years.

142
00:07:11,500 --> 00:07:12,780
We're family,

143
00:07:13,860 --> 00:07:15,060
and you have me.

144
00:07:16,180 --> 00:07:18,140
I won't let you bear it alone anymore.

145
00:07:19,020 --> 00:07:20,140
And I believe

146
00:07:20,620 --> 00:07:22,300
we will find evidence

147
00:07:23,020 --> 00:07:26,860
to clear both our fathers' names.

148
00:07:52,420 --> 00:07:53,260
Alright.

149
00:07:56,020 --> 00:07:57,220
You have me.

150
00:08:00,180 --> 00:08:01,020
No more tears.

151
00:08:02,300 --> 00:08:03,780
Now that Su Jue knows

152
00:08:04,100 --> 00:08:05,300
my father is here,

153
00:08:06,780 --> 00:08:08,700
