158
00:08:18,140 --> 00:08:20,060
How about staying at my place?

159
00:08:20,340 --> 00:08:21,260
Your place?

160
00:08:21,610 --> 00:08:22,460
Dandan and I

161
00:08:22,460 --> 00:08:25,140
have a quiet house in Xifang Alley.

162
00:08:26,180 --> 00:08:27,540
It's simple,

163
00:08:27,980 --> 00:08:29,540
but it's livable.

164
00:08:32,420 --> 00:08:34,540
I'll move there with the master.

165
00:08:35,140 --> 00:08:36,140
With me there,

166
00:08:36,340 --> 00:08:38,260
the master will have someone to look after him.

167
00:08:39,340 --> 00:08:40,180
Thank you.

168
00:08:59,140 --> 00:09:00,060
You're awake.

169
00:09:00,300 --> 00:09:01,540
Shuangshuang.

170
00:09:02,500 --> 00:09:03,620
Are you okay?

171
00:09:03,980 --> 00:09:05,340
Of course, I'm okay.

172
00:09:05,620 --> 00:09:06,620
But you...

173
00:09:06,620 --> 00:09:07,820
Why did you push yourself?

174
00:09:08,980 --> 00:09:09,820
Well.

175
00:09:10,020 --> 00:09:11,380
I was worried about you

176
00:09:11,580 --> 00:09:13,740
and wanted to be your protector.

177
00:09:13,740 --> 00:09:14,940
This is no time

178
00:09:14,940 --> 00:09:16,500
for jokes.

179
00:09:22,140 --> 00:09:23,180
My leg...

180
00:09:23,180 --> 00:09:24,140
I've contacted

181
00:09:24,140 --> 00:09:25,740
the best doctor, Doctor Qu.

182
00:09:25,740 --> 00:09:26,740
He'll be here soon.

183
00:09:28,180 --> 00:09:30,420
