184
00:09:30,620 --> 00:09:31,900
Don't talk like that.

185
00:09:32,540 --> 00:09:34,380
Doctor Qu is the best healer.

186
00:09:34,380 --> 00:09:35,620
He will find a way.

187
00:09:35,860 --> 00:09:37,980
Even if my leg can't be healed,

188
00:09:38,780 --> 00:09:41,140
it's worth trading my legs

189
00:09:41,820 --> 00:09:42,780
for your safety.

190
00:09:43,660 --> 00:09:45,140
Don't blame yourself.

191
00:09:50,420 --> 00:09:51,420
Thank you.

192
00:10:00,860 --> 00:10:01,700
Please.

193
00:10:02,100 --> 00:10:03,020
Doctor Qu.

194
00:10:04,100 --> 00:10:05,300
Let me see.

195
00:10:05,300 --> 00:10:06,220
Young Master.

196
00:10:06,540 --> 00:10:08,540
If my legs don't heal,

197
00:10:08,980 --> 00:10:11,380
I won't be able to serve you anymore.

198
00:10:11,380 --> 00:10:12,460
Don't talk nonsense.

199
00:10:13,060 --> 00:10:14,180
If your legs really can't heal,

200
00:10:14,180 --> 00:10:15,740
I'll take care of you
for the rest of your life.

201
