All his bones are shattered.

202
00:10:26,500 --> 00:10:27,700
What should we do now?

203
00:10:27,900 --> 00:10:29,860
I can only set the bones by hand.

204
00:10:30,460 --> 00:10:32,340
When he can barely stand,

205
00:10:32,340 --> 00:10:33,460
he'll need exercise

206
00:10:33,460 --> 00:10:34,820
to recover.

207
00:10:34,820 --> 00:10:35,740
Firstly,

208
00:10:35,740 --> 00:10:37,460
his bones are badly shattered.

209
00:10:37,460 --> 00:10:40,100
I can only align them by touch.

210
00:10:40,300 --> 00:10:42,020
I can't guarantee perfect alignment.

211
00:10:42,020 --> 00:10:43,100
Even if he stands,

212
00:10:43,300 --> 00:10:45,300
he'll still have a limp.

213
00:10:45,980 --> 00:10:46,820
Secondly,

214
00:10:47,020 --> 00:10:48,820
the pain of setting shattered bones

215
00:10:48,820 --> 00:10:50,300
is unbearable.

216
00:10:50,300 --> 00:10:52,580
He will suffer greatly.

217
00:10:52,580 --> 00:10:54,540
You are the doctor Shuangshuang trusts,

218
00:10:55,060 --> 00:10:56,300
so I trust you too.

219
00:10:57,100 --> 00:10:58,060
Let's begin.

220
00:11:13,260 --> 00:11:14,620
He can't watch this.

