222
00:11:17,740 --> 00:11:18,580
OK.

223
00:11:24,700 --> 00:11:26,100
I can't do it.

224
00:11:26,620 --> 00:11:27,980
I don't want the treatment.

225
00:11:31,460 --> 00:11:32,780
Let me go.

226
00:11:32,780 --> 00:11:33,620
Kill me.

227
00:11:33,900 --> 00:11:34,740
It hurts.

228
00:11:35,220 --> 00:11:36,140
It hurts.

229
00:11:41,940 --> 00:11:43,300
Liu, you have to hold on.

230
00:11:46,580 --> 00:11:47,420
It hurts.

231
00:11:48,820 --> 00:11:50,060
I don't want it.

232
00:11:50,420 --> 00:11:52,060
I don't want it.

233
00:11:52,060 --> 00:11:55,260
Let me go.

234
00:12:12,500 --> 00:12:13,420
It hurts.

235
00:12:49,260 --> 00:12:50,100
It's done.

236
00:12:55,580 --> 00:12:57,420
Let me check your pulse again.

237
00:13:03,820 --> 00:13:04,660
How is he?

238
00:13:05,940 --> 00:13:07,460
Don't worry. It was successful.

239
00:13:12,660 --> 00:13:13,500
By the way,

240
00:13:14,020 --> 00:13:16,260
I think I found...

241
00:13:22,980 --> 00:13:27,660
(Peace and Tranquility)

242
00:13:27,660 --> 00:13:30,100
Is this the legendary water amber?

243
00:13:31,420 --> 00:13:32,260
Yes.

244
00:13:32,700 --> 00:13:34,380
It disappeared completely

245
00:13:34,380 --> 00:13:35,980
after the Crown was lost.

246
00:13:36,260 --> 00:13:37,100
I can't believe

247
00:13:37,300 --> 00:13:38,900
it's been hanging around your neck.

248
00:13:39,900 --> 00:13:43,140
Why was it encased in alum?

249
00:13:43,700 --> 00:13:45,420
I heard from my mother

250
00:13:46,500 --> 00:13:48,900
that water amber is extremely precious.

251
00:13:49,260 --> 00:13:51,060
If exposed for too long,

252
00:13:51,060 --> 00:13:52,260
it would rust,

253
00:13:52,260 --> 00:13:54,300
forming a surface like an egg.

254
00:13:54,300 --> 00:13:55,220
Because of this,

255
00:13:55,580 --> 00:13:57,540
my father encased it in a glass shell

256
00:13:57,540 --> 00:13:59,580
and placed it on the Crown.

257
00:13:59,940 --> 00:14:02,220
The Crown's top was detachable,

258
00:14:02,540 --> 00:14:04,620
so it could be easily removed by the Emperor.

259
00:14:04,940 --> 00:14:07,060
The glass shell must have been broken,

260
00:14:07,060 --> 00:14:08,580
so it was encased in alum.

261
00:14:09,100 --> 00:14:10,180
I never expected

262
00:14:10,540 --> 00:14:12,180
Guard Zhao to hide it

263
00:14:12,180 --> 00:14:13,700
on Dandan all this time.

264
00:14:15,020 --> 00:14:16,300
For years,

265
00:14:16,300 --> 00:14:17,300
I've been searching

266
00:14:17,300 --> 00:14:19,540
for the other half of the Crown and its jewels.

267
00:14:20,340 --> 00:14:22,860
Now it seems laughable.

268
00:14:29,860 --> 00:14:31,020
If I'm correct,

269
00:14:31,300 --> 00:14:32,940
with the loss of the water amber,

270
00:14:33,580 --> 00:14:34,700
the other half of the Crown

271
00:14:35,100 --> 00:14:36,740
must have been lost

272
00:14:37,420 --> 00:14:38,700
in the wilderness during the fight.

273
00:14:39,900 --> 00:14:41,220
Or it's

274
00:14:41,540 --> 00:14:42,380
with the Su family.

275
00:14:42,940 --> 00:14:44,660
The Crown has always been in their hands,

276
00:14:44,660 --> 00:14:46,420
but they couldn't decipher it

277
00:14:47,580 --> 00:14:49,180
and caused others' families to be destroyed.

278
00:14:50,020 --> 00:14:51,100
Despicable.

279
00:14:57,540 --> 00:14:58,380
How is he?

280
00:14:58,780 --> 00:15:00,020
He's taken my medicine

281
00:15:00,020 --> 00:15:01,340
and is sleeping.

282
00:15:01,340 --> 00:15:03,100
You can rest easy now.

283
00:15:03,300 --> 00:15:04,500
I owe you a great debt of gratitude.

284
00:15:04,500 --> 00:15:06,660
Please accept my bow.

285
00:15:06,660 --> 00:15:07,620
You silly girl.

286
00:15:07,940 --> 00:15:09,580
How many times have I told you

287
00:15:09,580 --> 00:15:10,980
not to mention gratitude to me?

288
00:15:13,420 --> 00:15:14,300
Doctor Qu,

289
00:15:14,980 --> 00:15:16,420
I have another request.

290
00:15:16,780 --> 00:15:17,620
What is it?

291
00:15:18,260 --> 00:15:20,340
Another patient needs your help.

292
00:15:20,540 --> 00:15:21,860
I'm exhausted today.

293
00:15:21,860 --> 00:15:23,140
Let me rest,

294
00:15:23,140 --> 00:15:25,180
and we'll discuss it tomorrow.

295
00:15:25,180 --> 00:15:27,820
Alright, I'll visit you tomorrow.

296
00:15:29,540 --> 00:15:30,380
Thank you.

297
00:15:35,820 --> 00:15:38,300
You want him to treat Master Pei's madness?

298
00:15:39,860 --> 00:15:41,900
You totally get me.

299
00:15:43,060 --> 00:15:44,180
Can he really be cured?

300
00:15:44,180 --> 00:15:45,860
Let's have Doctor Qu try.

301
00:15:46,540 --> 00:15:48,540
If he can't do it,

302
00:15:48,540 --> 00:15:50,060
no one can.

303
00:15:54,380 --> 00:15:56,820
(Suyu Pavilion)

304
00:15:58,500 --> 00:16:00,100
The precision of this knife work

305
00:16:00,100 --> 00:16:02,500
is remarkable for just a few months
of practice.

306
00:16:03,580 --> 00:16:05,660
I've spent my whole life studying it.

307
00:16:05,940 --> 00:16:07,340
What am I lacking?

308
00:16:15,220 --> 00:16:16,060
How's it going?

309
00:16:16,380 --> 00:16:18,340
Young Master, as you suspected,

310
00:16:18,340 --> 00:16:20,300
the Pei's family sent someone out overnight,

311
00:16:20,300 --> 00:16:21,900
but at the alley in the North Market,

312
00:16:21,900 --> 00:16:22,980
they split into two groups.

313
00:16:23,620 --> 00:16:25,140
The alleyways are intricate,

314
00:16:25,500 --> 00:16:27,340
and the hired trackers lost them.

315
00:16:27,540 --> 00:16:28,380
Useless!

316
00:16:28,580 --> 00:16:29,700
Please calm down.

317
00:16:29,900 --> 00:16:31,540
We've confirmed they are in that area.

318
00:16:31,540 --> 00:16:32,980
Our men are searching through the night.

319
00:16:32,980 --> 00:16:34,100
We should find them soon.

320
00:16:34,100 --> 00:16:35,740
Once you find them, kill them.

321
00:16:36,260 --> 00:16:37,100
Yes.

322
00:16:41,100 --> 00:16:42,100
Pei Pei,

323
00:16:43,380 --> 00:16:44,740
your mistake

324
00:16:44,740 --> 00:16:46,500
was constantly opposing me.

325
00:17:12,620 --> 00:17:13,500
How's it going?

326
00:17:15,060 --> 00:17:15,900
Come on.

327
00:17:16,340 --> 00:17:17,420
Let's sit and discuss.

328
00:17:23,260 --> 00:17:26,140
He's been in a cold and damp place
for a long time.

329
00:17:26,140 --> 00:17:27,260
The dampness invaded his heart,

330
00:17:27,460 --> 00:17:29,060
and he suffered severe trauma,

331
00:17:29,060 --> 00:17:30,660
causing a mental breakdown.

332
00:17:31,780 --> 00:17:33,060
Is there a way to cure him?

333
00:17:33,620 --> 00:17:35,380
I can use acupuncture

334
00:17:35,380 --> 00:17:37,100
to expel the cold from his body.

335
00:17:37,100 --> 00:17:38,660
When his acupuncture points open,

336
00:17:38,980 --> 00:17:40,300
if we can use something

337
00:17:40,500 --> 00:17:42,500
that scares him

338
00:17:42,500 --> 00:17:43,580
to shock his mind,

339
00:17:44,100 --> 00:17:46,260
we might restore his sanity.

340
00:17:49,340 --> 00:17:50,540
Is there any danger?

341
00:17:50,540 --> 00:17:52,300
There's no life-threatening risk,

342
00:17:52,300 --> 00:17:54,460
but if it fails,

343
00:17:54,460 --> 00:17:57,380
his mental state may worsen.

344
00:18:08,060 --> 00:18:09,860
My father had a proud spirit.

345
00:18:10,260 --> 00:18:11,980
If given the choice,

346
00:18:12,300 --> 00:18:13,580
he would rather take the risk

347
00:18:13,900 --> 00:18:14,860
than live like this.

348
00:19:35,620 --> 00:19:36,900
The acupuncture is complete.

349
00:19:37,140 --> 00:19:40,420
Now, we begin the mental stimulation.

350
00:19:48,540 --> 00:19:49,620
Doctor, please proceed.

351
00:19:53,700 --> 00:19:54,540
Dad.

352
00:19:55,580 --> 00:19:56,420
Dad.

353
00:19:58,260 --> 00:19:59,340
It's me, Pei Pei.

354
00:20:08,540 --> 00:20:09,460
I'm Pei Pei.

355
00:20:09,980 --> 00:20:10,860
Your Pei.

356
00:20:11,540 --> 00:20:13,420
Do you remember me, Dad?

357
00:20:15,500 --> 00:20:17,420
Dad, it's Pei.

358
00:20:18,580 --> 00:20:19,700
Look at me.

359
00:20:20,060 --> 00:20:21,420
It's not enough.

360
00:20:28,340 --> 00:20:30,580
Perhaps I have a way.

361
00:20:42,220 --> 00:20:44,260
Is this the legendary Moonlight Crown?

362
00:20:55,580 --> 00:20:56,420
This...

363
00:21:07,980 --> 00:21:08,820
Dad,

364
00:21:10,500 --> 00:21:11,460
look at this.

365
00:21:12,300 --> 00:21:13,500
Do you recognize it?

366
00:21:15,380 --> 00:21:16,740
You're lucky

367
00:21:17,500 --> 00:21:18,740
to survive this.

368
00:21:18,740 --> 00:21:20,260
Since you're still alive,

369
00:21:21,620 --> 00:21:23,460
you'll be used by us.

370
00:21:24,220 --> 00:21:25,260
Hungry?

371
00:21:25,260 --> 00:21:26,420
Then eat this.

372
00:21:31,500 --> 00:21:32,820
- Master!
- Dad!

373
00:21:33,140 --> 00:21:33,980
Dad.

374
00:21:34,060 --> 00:21:34,900
Dad.

375
00:21:35,100 --> 00:21:35,940
Dad.

376
00:21:36,660 --> 00:21:37,540
What's happening?

377
00:21:38,700 --> 00:21:39,780
It's nothing serious.

378
00:21:39,780 --> 00:21:40,940
He's just fainted.

379
00:21:41,220 --> 00:21:42,780
Let him lie down.

380
00:21:50,060 --> 00:21:51,180
I'm truly sorry.

381
00:21:51,180 --> 00:21:53,620
I did my best.

382
00:21:53,980 --> 00:21:55,220
This was our choice.

383
00:21:55,900 --> 00:21:57,020
Not your fault.

384
00:21:57,580 --> 00:21:59,100
Will he be in danger?

385
00:21:59,100 --> 00:22:00,500
He's weakened,

386
00:22:00,780 --> 00:22:03,900
and he'll need time to recover his strength,

387
00:22:03,900 --> 00:22:05,420
but he won't be in any danger.

388
00:22:05,420 --> 00:22:06,460
Rest assured.

389
00:22:08,140 --> 00:22:09,420
You've worked hard today.

390
00:22:09,700 --> 00:22:10,940
Please rest.

391
00:22:13,100 --> 00:22:13,980
I'll see you out.

392
00:22:17,300 --> 00:22:18,140
Farewell.

393
00:22:18,420 --> 00:22:19,540
Take care, Doctor.

394
00:22:27,900 --> 00:22:28,740
Don't worry.

395
00:22:29,380 --> 00:22:30,740
The master will be fine.

396
00:22:35,020 --> 00:22:35,940
Let me.

397
00:22:38,700 --> 00:22:41,500
The master dedicated his life to his work

398
00:22:41,500 --> 00:22:43,180
but now he's like this.

399
00:22:43,180 --> 00:22:45,420
He's still free from all worries.

400
00:22:45,940 --> 00:22:48,220
Maybe this is a release for him.

401
00:22:59,700 --> 00:23:00,540
Pei.

402
00:23:03,820 --> 00:23:04,900
Pei.

403
00:23:07,860 --> 00:23:08,780
Pei.

404
00:23:09,060 --> 00:23:10,140
Dad, I'm here.

405
00:23:11,900 --> 00:23:13,140
- Pei.
- Dad.

406
00:23:13,940 --> 00:23:14,780
Here.

407
00:23:18,580 --> 00:23:19,620
I'm Pei.

408
00:23:20,100 --> 00:23:21,100
Do you recognize me now?

409
00:23:22,820 --> 00:23:24,300
You've grown so much.

410
00:23:24,820 --> 00:23:25,660
Dad.

411
00:23:30,180 --> 00:23:31,140
Pei.

412
00:23:33,540 --> 00:23:34,380
Dad.

413
00:23:55,860 --> 00:23:57,060
Liu, time to eat.

414
00:23:57,060 --> 00:23:57,900
Thank you.

415
00:24:00,380 --> 00:24:01,220
Shuangshuang,

416
00:24:02,020 --> 00:24:03,820
I'm so happy to see you

417
00:24:04,100 --> 00:24:05,340
back with us.

418
00:24:08,940 --> 00:24:10,500
Honestly, I never thought...

419
00:24:10,500 --> 00:24:12,220
Master Pei would come back alive

420
00:24:12,220 --> 00:24:13,620
and cured.

421
00:24:13,620 --> 00:24:14,860
Heaven is truly watching over us.

422
00:24:18,180 --> 00:24:19,020
Yes.

423
00:24:20,380 --> 00:24:22,540
I want to help now,

424
00:24:22,860 --> 00:24:24,580
but I'm bedridden with broken bones.

425
00:24:24,580 --> 00:24:26,020
There's nothing I can help.

426
00:24:26,020 --> 00:24:27,700
Just focus on recovering.

427
00:24:27,700 --> 00:24:29,460
Don't worry about anything.

428
00:24:31,860 --> 00:24:32,700
Who's there?

429
00:25:06,820 --> 00:25:07,660
Speak up!

430
00:25:07,820 --> 00:25:09,460
Are you sent by Su Jue?

431
00:25:24,780 --> 00:25:26,420
Dad, let's eat.

432
00:25:27,100 --> 00:25:28,700
Master, take it slow.

433
00:25:32,100 --> 00:25:33,300
Master, have a seat.

434
00:25:39,700 --> 00:25:40,820
Who is this?

435
00:25:41,140 --> 00:25:43,020
I'm Dandan from Qipei Pavilion.

436
00:25:43,020 --> 00:25:43,860
Dad,

437
00:25:43,900 --> 00:25:46,140
Dandan is now Qipei Pavilion's shopkeeper

438
00:25:46,540 --> 00:25:47,740
and also

439
00:25:48,500 --> 00:25:49,420
my fiancée.

440
00:25:51,300 --> 00:25:52,660
- Have a seat.
- OK.

441
00:25:53,900 --> 00:25:54,740
OK.

442
00:25:54,750 --> 00:25:55,980
More importantly,

443
00:25:56,220 --> 00:25:58,100
she is Guard Zhao's daughter.

444
00:25:58,380 --> 00:25:59,220
What?

445
00:25:59,260 --> 00:26:01,420
Ms. Dandan is Guard Zhao's daughter.

446
00:26:07,980 --> 00:26:10,780
Guard Zhao died protecting me.

447
00:26:10,780 --> 00:26:12,780
Now, you're part of our family.

448
00:26:12,780 --> 00:26:14,100
Perhaps it's a chance given by gods

449
00:26:14,100 --> 00:26:15,900
for us to repay him.

450
00:26:17,260 --> 00:26:18,660
Let's eat.

451
00:26:22,260 --> 00:26:23,100
Dandan.

452
00:26:24,820 --> 00:26:25,860
Shuangshuang, you're back.

453
00:26:26,660 --> 00:26:27,740
Are you all okay?

454
00:26:28,500 --> 00:26:29,340
We're fine.

455
00:26:29,620 --> 00:26:30,700
Sit and eat.

456
00:26:32,380 --> 00:26:34,180
Is Liu settled in?

457
00:26:35,180 --> 00:26:36,020
Thank you.

458
00:26:36,380 --> 00:26:39,060
Pei, who is this young lady?

459
00:26:39,940 --> 00:26:41,500
This is Ms. Shuangshuang.

460
00:26:42,500 --> 00:26:45,060
Her father is Shan Jingtian,

461
00:26:45,060 --> 00:26:46,420
who was deceived into stealing the Crown.

462
00:26:46,420 --> 00:26:47,260
What?

463
00:26:48,660 --> 00:26:49,860
That incident involved

464
00:26:49,860 --> 00:26:51,580
so many innocent people.

465
00:26:52,100 --> 00:26:52,940
What's more despicable

466
00:26:52,940 --> 00:26:54,340
is that these children were dragged into it

467
00:26:54,340 --> 00:26:56,740
over the years.

468
00:26:58,780 --> 00:26:59,780
I shouldn't say this

469
00:27:00,100 --> 00:27:02,660
in front of the children,

470
00:27:02,660 --> 00:27:04,700
but I must speak my mind.

471
00:27:05,180 --> 00:27:06,500
Eighteen years ago,

472
00:27:06,700 --> 00:27:08,820
Su Zhiyan, for his own gain,

473
00:27:08,820 --> 00:27:10,580
tried to steal the Crown.

474
00:27:10,980 --> 00:27:12,940
Despite his elaborate plans,

475
00:27:13,140 --> 00:27:14,500
he got nothing.

476
00:27:15,820 --> 00:27:17,100
The Crown

477
00:27:18,100 --> 00:27:20,900
was broken and lost.

478
00:27:20,900 --> 00:27:21,900
If I have to blame someone,

479
00:27:22,260 --> 00:27:25,380
it's the Su family for their wickedness.

480
00:27:26,140 --> 00:27:27,020
But

481
00:27:27,020 --> 00:27:28,980
the Su family

482
00:27:28,980 --> 00:27:30,700
didn't stop there.

483
00:27:30,700 --> 00:27:32,900
They spread rumors,

484
00:27:32,900 --> 00:27:35,020
accusing me of stealing the Crown.

485
00:27:35,720 --> 00:27:36,580
They even threatened me

486
00:27:36,580 --> 00:27:39,060
with Qipei Pavilion's business,

487
00:27:39,780 --> 00:27:40,820
forcing me to let Pei

488
00:27:42,700 --> 00:27:45,180
quit the Jade Competition.

489
00:27:45,980 --> 00:27:46,820
Pei,

490
00:27:47,860 --> 00:27:49,620
I was a coward back then.

491
00:27:50,980 --> 00:27:52,660
I've failed you.

492
00:27:54,940 --> 00:27:55,780
Dad.

493
00:27:57,980 --> 00:27:58,940
In the end,

494
00:28:00,620 --> 00:28:02,900
Su Jue's uncle Wang Jiu

495
00:28:03,580 --> 00:28:06,220
set me up in the inn

496
00:28:07,340 --> 00:28:09,420
and locked me up for over a decade.

497
00:28:10,100 --> 00:28:13,340
I was suffering there,

498
00:28:13,340 --> 00:28:15,220
living like a crazy animal.

499
00:28:16,860 --> 00:28:17,700
Dad,

500
00:28:19,460 --> 00:28:21,060
that's water under the bridge.

501
00:28:21,060 --> 00:28:22,100
Let's not dwell on the past.

502
00:28:22,300 --> 00:28:24,300
We're reunited now.

503
00:28:24,540 --> 00:28:25,780
Let's enjoy this meal.

504
00:28:27,300 --> 00:28:28,140
Don't worry.

505
00:28:28,580 --> 00:28:30,860
I won't let the villains go unpunished.

506
00:28:30,860 --> 00:28:31,700
Alright.

507
00:28:32,340 --> 00:28:33,180
Come.

508
00:28:33,380 --> 00:28:34,540
Here, Dad.

509
00:28:34,540 --> 00:28:35,380
Eat first.

510
00:28:42,900 --> 00:28:44,340
Dandan, you go inside.

511
00:28:44,340 --> 00:28:45,180
Stay safe.

512
00:29:14,540 --> 00:29:15,660
Shuangshuang, are you alright?

513
00:29:17,460 --> 00:29:18,300
I'm fine.

514
00:29:19,380 --> 00:29:21,940
They're from the Su family
trying to silence Master Pei.

515
00:29:21,940 --> 00:29:23,700
I've subdued one at Pei's Mansion,

516
00:29:23,700 --> 00:29:24,700
but like the others,

517
00:29:24,700 --> 00:29:25,780
he bit his tongue

518
00:29:25,780 --> 00:29:27,100
to avoid exposure.

519
00:29:27,440 --> 00:29:28,280
Where should we go now?

520
00:29:28,290 --> 00:29:29,700
This place has been exposed.

521
00:29:30,300 --> 00:29:31,220
Let's return to Pei's Mansion.

522
00:29:35,980 --> 00:29:37,700
By the mandate of heaven.

523
00:29:37,980 --> 00:29:42,020
(Xuanzheng Hall)
To the Lord of Yuncui City.

524
00:29:42,020 --> 00:29:42,860
Useless.

525
00:29:42,900 --> 00:29:45,100
You can't even deal with a dying mad old man.

526
00:29:45,100 --> 00:29:46,420
What can you do for me?

527
00:29:47,160 --> 00:29:48,220
Young Master, please forgive me.

528
00:29:48,220 --> 00:29:50,060
I underestimated the Pei family.

529
00:29:50,060 --> 00:29:51,220
It was my oversight.

530
00:29:51,220 --> 00:29:52,780
Don't give me that crap.

531
00:29:53,060 --> 00:29:54,980
Tell me. What are you going to do now?

532
00:29:55,500 --> 00:29:57,300
Young Master, the City Lord summons you.

533
00:30:03,940 --> 00:30:04,940
Continue searching.

534
00:30:04,940 --> 00:30:06,460
If there's another mishap,

535
00:30:06,780 --> 00:30:09,500
you'll join those dead men.

536
00:30:25,380 --> 00:30:27,500
(Xuanzheng Hall)

537
00:30:27,500 --> 00:30:29,060
Greetings, Your Lordship.

538
00:30:29,420 --> 00:30:30,260
Rise.

539
00:30:32,780 --> 00:30:35,220
May I ask why you've summoned us so urgently?

540
00:30:41,100 --> 00:30:43,780
(Reforge the Moonlight Crown)

541
00:30:44,980 --> 00:30:45,820
This...

542
00:30:45,820 --> 00:30:46,860
You read correctly.

543
00:30:46,860 --> 00:30:47,860
The Empress is critically ill,

544
00:30:47,860 --> 00:30:50,420
and her only regret

545
00:30:50,420 --> 00:30:51,660
is not having the Moonlight Crown

546
00:30:51,660 --> 00:30:53,020
from years ago.

547
00:30:53,020 --> 00:30:55,220
The Emperor has sent an urgent decree,

548
00:30:55,460 --> 00:30:56,540
ordering us to quickly restore

549
00:30:56,540 --> 00:30:58,420
the Crown from the original design

550
00:30:58,620 --> 00:31:00,420
to fulfill the Empress' wish.

551
00:31:03,220 --> 00:31:04,060
Your Lordship,

552
00:31:04,500 --> 00:31:06,220
after Pei Chufeng

553
00:31:06,220 --> 00:31:07,620
embezzled the Crown,

554
00:31:07,620 --> 00:31:08,780
didn't we deliver

555
00:31:08,780 --> 00:31:10,420
another crown on time?

556
00:31:10,420 --> 00:31:12,300
Indeed, you accomplished the mission

557
00:31:12,300 --> 00:31:14,220
and delivered a substitute,

558
00:31:14,220 --> 00:31:16,300
saving us from the Emperor's wrath.

559
00:31:16,300 --> 00:31:17,300
But remember.

560
00:31:17,300 --> 00:31:18,660
The Empress was dissatisfied

561
00:31:18,660 --> 00:31:20,260
with that crown.

562
00:31:20,260 --> 00:31:22,380
She played with it briefly and discarded it.

563
00:31:22,660 --> 00:31:24,940
She didn't even wear it
on her birthday banquet.

564
00:31:24,940 --> 00:31:26,340
That's the Imperial Palace.

565
00:31:26,340 --> 00:31:27,740
They have everything.

566
00:31:27,740 --> 00:31:29,620
We can't just casually make do.

567
00:31:29,620 --> 00:31:30,820
But, Your Lordship,

568
00:31:31,220 --> 00:31:32,820
even Pei Chufeng,

569
00:31:32,820 --> 00:31:34,340
leading so many master craftsmen,

570
00:31:34,340 --> 00:31:36,780
took several months
to create the Moonlight Crown.

571
00:31:36,780 --> 00:31:38,940
Now, with the Empress critically ill
and time running out,

572
00:31:38,940 --> 00:31:40,260
- I fear...
- This is an imperial order,

573
00:31:40,260 --> 00:31:41,540
not a discussion.

574
00:31:43,180 --> 00:31:44,380
It's absurd,

575
00:31:44,620 --> 00:31:46,100
but in Yuncui City,

576
00:31:46,100 --> 00:31:47,340
the Suyu Pavilion

577
00:31:47,340 --> 00:31:48,620
is our only hope.

578
00:31:48,820 --> 00:31:50,060
No matter how,

579
00:31:50,060 --> 00:31:52,420
